### Retrieval Schemas

#### [NEW] [schemas.py](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/schemas.py)

Pydantic DTOs for retrieval input/output:

| Model | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `RetrievalRequest` | Input: locked SQO + initial K |
| `ScoredChunk` | Single chunk with all score components |
| `ScoreBreakdown` | Breakdown of weighted_score into 6 signals |
| `RetrievalResult` | Output: ranked chunks, final K, recall, stage diagnostics |
| `StageResult` | Per-stage diagnostic (candidate count, duration) |
| `RetrievalConfidence` | Confidence estimation for the retrieval pass |

